dataList.content: It is the same entity we repeatedly encountered during our passages through Dungeons and Refraction Railways, Manager.
<Which means we already know how to defeat it.>
Though our means of dealing with it may mirror what has come prior, Dante, complacency would ill serve us.
With the current disorder permeating this place, Qliphoth Deterrence may fail to function reliably...
So we gotta stay sharp during the fight... I get it. Sora, Ravi—get behind me, okay?
